Name: Zenkat
About the game: Welcome to ZenKat! A game that can take 10 minutes or 10 years to complete depending on your ability to remain determined and focused. Play as the ZenKat, the guardian of time and space in the realm of oriental felines, an immortal cat that is always willing to give it another shot as long as it's instructor is willing to persevere. Help ZenKat by finishing all of his puzzling tasks and finding out what lies at the end of the Realm of Elements.
